<plot>"The Pipe Dream" follows the rapid climb to success of Whistler half pipe snowboarders, Crispin Lipscomb and Dan Raymond. The filmmaker follows their journeys from hard working snowboard instructors to joining the National Team, gold medals at international competitions, sponsorship endorsements, and finally reaching for Olympic gold at the 2006 Olympic Games in Torino, Italy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?582783</url></doc>
